{"tid":2133255,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃家和：望食肆可有序恢復堂食包括晚市","createTime":"2020-07-31T03:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T04:48:07.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b884a45f85e461d6e625cfda1a920cc06616a73e","tid":2133255,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"黃家和：望食肆可有序恢復堂食包括晚市<br />\n27分鐘前<br />\n<br />\n&quot;【Now新聞台】香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和指，全日禁堂食令業界生意大跌八成，政府撤回全日禁堂食限制是明智之舉，希望食肆可有序地恢復堂食，包括晚市。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=399984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399984&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG18jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=c8f6d3d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D399984&h=e94b85ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=399984</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">香港市民的共同願望(恐懼撚除外)</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4efa7d8b597244a52fb70f13f726e05574ac562d","tid":2133255,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T03:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>唐太宗活洛油！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"719d6ab968cf151223e427fe590c04ae1ed9479d","tid":2133255,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T08:44:43.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n<br />\n今日確診數字明顯回落<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541038-20200731.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541038-20200731.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG18jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=9766069d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541038-20200731.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ab977549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541038-20200731.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"5bc9c5bbdf0625d247dcb9da1f824aad50dcb254","tid":2133255,"uid":166845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T04:48:07.000Z","msg":"黃家和，漢族，香港商人。<br />\n<br />\n生平<br />\n父親是著名咖啡批發商捷榮集團創辦人黃橋先生[1]。黃家和自小已參予家族生意，並曾任捷榮集團行政總裁。在1993年自立門戶，創立金百加集團。<br />\n<br />\n在2018年山竹風災過後，有政黨提出私人條例草案，建議政府立法「停工令」。香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和出席《城市論壇》時表示，「得閒過頭、冇野做，得閒就講立法」，並反對立法草案，並表示颱風翌日自己（開車）到公司只比平日多花半小時。 任政協黑龍江省委員會委員[2]、金百加集團主席、香港餐飲聯業協會會長[3]、太平紳士[4]、香港食品及飲品行業總會主席、品牌發展局主席[5][6][7][8][9]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2584%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2592%258C_&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG18jWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=f6305738\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%84%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C_</a>(%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA)"}]}